<br>
This puts the name text outside the area of the playerwindow, effectively removing it from the box.  You may note this is also done defaultly with the pet hp bar - the TextOffsetX is set to -50 there, and the pet's name doesn't show, so presumably you could just do that as well, but it doesn't hurt to be safe with -250 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
